ulence when they are injected into G. melonella larvae.},
author = {Marokh{\'{a}}zi, Judit and Lengyel, Katalin and Pek{\'{a}}r, Szilvia and Felf{\"{o}}ldi, Gabriella and Patthy, Andr{\'{a}}s and Gr{\'{a}}f, L{\'{a}}szl{\'{o}} and Fodor, Andr{\'{a}}s and Venekei, Istv{\'{a}}n},
